\v 44 Neho Y…®…®su akatan Čra k Čh…®t…®ra Yudeya,\f + \fr 4:44 \fk Yudeya\ft , Zibhibhuriya …®z…®nd…® z…®rabhuga, \fqa Gariraaya.\f* ararwaz…®ra abhaat Č m Čmarwaz…®r Č. 
\c 5  
\s1 Y…®…®su aratanga korobhora abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® 
