\p  
\v 1 Rusik Č r Čmw…®, Y…®…®su aar…® imiiriir…® rusiz Č w…® …®nyanza ya Genezar…®ti,\f + \fr 5:1 \fk ∆ónyanza ya Genezar…®ti \ft iriina …®r…®nd…®, …®nyanza ya Gariraaya.\f* …®n Č ariija riribhita rya abhaat Č …®ng ľana ya Mungu. Bhakabha bharamwisuk…®ra, korereke bhamwigw…®, kuhika bhakamurimbya.  
\v 2 Na rusiz Č w…® …®nyanza hayo, Y…®…®su akarora ubhwat Č abh…®r…®, abhaw…®s…®ni bhaar…® bharuur…® mubhwat Č, bharooja zenzero zaabh Č.  
\v 3 Akatiira mubhwat Č bh Čmw…®, bh Čn Č bhwar…® bhwa Sim Č Čni, akasabha Sim Č Čni abhuhir…® kore hasuuhu m Čnyanza. Y…®…®su aar…® achamariirya k Čbharag…®r…®ra abhaat Č, …®n Č iik…®…®r…® mubhwat Č. 
