\v 12 Han Č Y…®…®su aar…® m Čr Čbh…®ri r Čmw…®, akaaza  Čm Č Čt Č w Čmw…® w Čn Č aar…® ne ebhegenge m Čbh…®r…® gw Čsi. Han Č  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo aar Č Čz…® Y…®…®su, akamugw…®ra m Čmag Čr Č, akiisasaama, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č,  Čraas…®…®g…®,  Črat Čra k Čmb…®ngukya.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Y…®…®su akagorora okobhoko kwaz…®, akamukun ľyaku, akam Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúN…®s…®…®gir…®. Bh…®ngukibhwa!‚ÄĚ Hayohayo, akahora ebhegenge bhyaz…®. 
\p  
\v 14 Y…®…®su akamorecha, ‚Äú…Ątabh Č Čr…®ra m Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi! Nawe, nuuj…® wiiyeereken ľye kwa kuhaani, uhuruch…® ikimweso ch Č  Čk Čbh…®ngukibhwa kwaz Č, ch…®mbu Musa aaswajiry…®, kwerecha abhaat Č k Čbha  Čbh…®ngukiibhw…®.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 5:14 \ft K Čr…®ng ľaana ni imigir Č ja Musa, kuhaani newe aar…® aramenyeekererya k Čbha  Čm Č Čt Č abh…®ngukiibhw…® ebhegenge. \xt Rora Abharaawi 14:1‚ÄĎ32; Amahiity Č gi Imigir Č 24:8.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Nawe, …®ng ľana ya Y…®…®su …®kang ľeha komenyekana bh Čk Čng ľu k Čbhaat Č. Bhaar…® bharamujaku maribhita maaru, bhabhone kwitegeerera imigir Č jaz…®, na k Čh Čribhwa amarw…®r…® gaabh Č.  
\v 16 Nawe, Y…®…®su aar…® arabhatiga na kuja ahagero han Č hataana abhaat Č k Čsabha Mungu. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arahorya  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č akuur…® ibhiim Č 
\r (Mataayo 9:1‚ÄĎ8; Maaroko 2:1‚ÄĎ12) 
\p  
\v 17 Rusik Č r Čmw…®, Y…®…®su aar…® ariija abhaat Č, na gat…® waabh Č bhaar…® bhiik…®…®r…® Abhafarisaayo,\f + \fr 5:17a \fk Abhafarisaayo\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* hamw…®mw…® na abhiija bhi imigir Č.\f + \fr 5:17b \fk Abhiija bhi imigir Č\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* Bhaar…® bharuur…® m Čz…®mb…®ri za Gariraaya, Yudeya, na abhand…® Y…®rusar…®…®mu. Y…®…®su aar…® n Č  Čbh Čnaja bhw Č …Ąm Čk Čr Č Mungu bhwo okohorya abharw…®r…®. 
\p  
\v 18 Neho bhakaaza abhaat Č bhag…®gir…®  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č aar…® akuur…® ibhiim Č, ahindiir…® k Čk…®rag Č. Bhakeenda kumusikirya munyumba, korereke bham Čt Č Čr…® m Čbh Čtang…® bhwa Y…®…®su.  
\v 19 Nawe …®tat Čr…®k…®…®n…®, k Č k Čbha ya riribhita ik Čr Č. Neho bhakatiira kwitiir…®r Č, bhakahika kwirengo ryi inyumba, bhag…®gir…®  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo. Han Č bhaar…® ig Čr Č, bhakahobhora …®k…®bhanga k…®k Čr Č, bhakaruusha  Čbh Čnyaaki k Čk…®sara,\f + \fr 5:19 \ft Abhayaahudi abhand…® bhaar…® bharasereeta zinyumba zaabh Č ku ukuhindirya z…®mbao ig Čr Č, bhakaz…®t Č Čr…®ra kwitiir…®r Č. Rora ipicha \xt Maaroko 2:4\ft .\f* bhakamwicha m Čbh Čtang…® bhwa Y…®…®su, gat…® wa abhaat Č bhayo bh Č Čsi.  
\v 20 Han Č Y…®…®su aar Č Čz…® ubhwisirirya bhwabh Č, akam Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúM Čsaani waan…®, ihaana umw Čy Č,  Čbh Čbh…® bhwaz Č bh Čbh…®…®r…®…®rw…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 21 Abhiija bhi imigir Č na Abhafarisaayo bhayo, rogendo r Čmw…® bhakatanga k Čr…®r…®…®r…®ra mumy Čy Č, ‚ÄúN…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…® wuyo? Ndora aragamba amang ľana go okorega Mungu? Atareeho  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č ak Čt Čra kobheerera  Čbh Čbh…®, nawe Mungu umwene!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 22 Y…®…®su akamenya gan Č bhaar…® bhakwiseega, akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúKwak…® muriiseegabhu mumy Čy Č janyu?  
\v 23 Aw…®, ni‚ÄĎryahe riny Č Čhu, k Čm Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚Äė…Ąbh Čbh…® bhwaz Č bh Čbh…®…®r…®…®rw…®,‚Äô kisha k Čm Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄėIm…®…®r…®ra, ogende‚Äô?  
\v 24 Iny…® nereenda momenye bhwaheene k Čbha, Umwana w Č …Ąm Č Čt Č\f + \fr 5:24 \fk Umwana w Č …Ąm Č Čt Č \ft ni‚ÄĎriina …®r…®nd…® rya Y…®…®su, ariigamb…®ra umwene. K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* ah…®…®rw…®  Čbh Čnaja bhwo okobheerera  Čbh Čbh…® k Č Čs…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p Ak Čmara Y…®…®su akabh Č Čr…®ra  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo, ‚ÄúN…®rak Čbh Č Čr…®ra, im…®…®r…®ra! Gega …®k…®rag Č chaz Č, ogende y…®…®ka.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 25 Hayohayo,  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo akiim…®…®r…®ra m Čbh Čtang…® bhwa abhaat Č bhayo. Akiitw…®ka …®k…®rag Č chaz…® k…®n Č aar…® ahindiriir…®, akaja munyumba, …®n Č arag Čnga Mungu.  
\v 26 Abhaat Č bh Č Čsi bhayo, bhakar Čg Č Čra bh Čk Čng ľu na kugwatwa nu ubhw Čbha. Hamw…®mw…® na gayo, bhaar…® bharag Čnga Mungu, bharabhuga, ‚ÄúBhamura! Reero, t Čr Č Čz…® amahyoro!‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabh…®r…®k…®ra Raawi amutun…® 
\r (Mataayo 9:9‚ÄĎ13; Maaroko 2:13‚ÄĎ17) 
\p  
\v 27 Han Č gayo gaasirir…®, Y…®…®su akarwa munyumba, akarora umurihya wa rig Č Čti w Čmw…®, iriina ryaz…® Raawi, aar…® ik…®…®r…® mwibhuru ryu ukurihya rig Č Čti. Y…®…®su akam Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúNtuna!‚ÄĚ\fig Umurihya wa rig Č Čti|alt="Mtoza ushuru" src="GT00045.tif" size="col" loc="LUK 5:27" copy="Gordon Thompson ¬© 2012 Wycliffe Bible Translators, Inc." ref="5:27" \fig* 
\v 28 Rogendo r Čmw…® akiim…®…®r…®ra, akatiga bhy Čsi, akamutuna. 
\p  
\v 29 Ak Čmara, Raawi akakorera Y…®…®su …®nyangi k Čr Č munyumba yaaz…®. Munyumba muyo, bhakiibhiringa abharihya bha rig Č Čti bhaaru, na abhaat Č abhand…® bhan Č bhaar…® bhararya igari r…®mw…®.  
\v 30 ∆ókagirya Abhafarisaayo, na abhiija bhaabh Č bhi imigir Č, bhakaja kwibheerya k Čbh…®…®ga bha Y…®…®su, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúNdora m Črarya na kunywa hamw…®mw…® na abharihya bha rig Č Čti na abhak Čri bh Č  Čbh Čbh…®?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 31 Y…®…®su akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúAbhaat Č abhah Čru bhatakwenda  Čm Čgabh Č, nawe abharw…®r…® nebho bhakumwenda!  
\v 32 Iny…® nitiizir…® k Čbh…®r…®k…®ra bhe eheene, nawe bh Č  Čbh Čbh…®, bhiich Čr…®r…® Mungu.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su, n…®‚ÄĎbh Čtang…® bhwa amang ľana amahya 
\r (Mataayo 9:14‚ÄĎ17; Maaroko 2:18‚ÄĎ22) 
\p  
\v 33 Abhafarisaayo na abhiija bhi migir Č, bhakabh Č Čr…®ra Y…®…®su, ‚ÄúAbh…®…®ga bha Yoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi bhariiyima kurya manga kaaru na k Čsabha Mungu. Na abh…®…®ga bha Abhafarisaayo, bh Č Čsi bhahaakorabhu. Nawe abh…®…®ga bhaaz Č, bhatakwiyima, bhararya na kunywa!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 34 Y…®…®su akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúAbhah…®r…®…®k…®r…®ri bhu umukw…®ri bhaheenderwa kwiyima kurya, bhar…® hamw…®mw…® nu umukw…®ri?  
\v 35 Nawe urusik Č r Čraaza umukw…®ri araruusibhwa gat…® wa abhagini bhaaz…®. Muzisik Č ziyo, neho bhak Čbha bhariiyima kurya.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 36 Y…®…®su akabhabh Č Čr…®ra ekerenjo …®k…®nd…®, ‚Äú…Ąk Čsanja amiija gaan…® amahya na zisim Čka zaanyu k Čratuubhana n Č  Čk Čt Č Čra …®k…®raka che engebho iihya kongebho ikungu. N Č  Čm Č Čt Č araakorebhu, arabha atarandwir…® engebho yaaz…® bh Č Čha. N…® …®k…®raka kirya che engebho iihya k…®takwisiriran ľya ne engebho ikungu. 
\p  
\v 37 ‚ÄúNa atareeho  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č ak Čt Čra k Čt Č Čra idivaayi\f + \fr 5:37 \fk Idivaayi\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* iihya m Čbh…®g Čzi bhya amaseero amakungu. Na araakorebhu, idivaayi iihya …®raatya …®bh…®g Čzi bhiyo, iriit…®ka, n…® …®bh…®g Čzi bhiyo bh…®rasar…®ka.  
