\v 29 Abhaat Č bh Č Čsi, hamw…®mw…® na abharihya bha rig Č Čti, han Č bhiigwir…® amang ľana ga Y…®…®su gayo, bhakiisirirya k Čbha …®s…®…®mi ya Mungu yaar…® nz Čmu, k Č k Čbha abhaat Č bhayo nebho bharya Yoohana amarir…® k Čbhatiiza.  
\v 30 Nawe, Abhafarisaayo na abhiija bhi imigir Č bhataabhatiizirw…® na Yoohana, k Č k Čbha bhakaanga amiis…®…®gi ga Mungu. 
\p  
\v 31 Y…®…®su akabhuga naatu, ‚ÄúAbhaat Č bhu urwibh Čr Č r Čn Č, n…®bhatuubhan ľy…® nak…®? N…®‚ÄĎbha teemwak…®?  
\v 32 Bhatuubh…®…®n…® na abhaana bhan Č bhiik…®…®r…® momoteera, bhakwibh…®r…®k…®ra abheene kobheene bharabhuga, ‚ÄėT Čkabhatemera ekereere, nawe m Čtaabhinir…®! T Čk…®…®mba am…®…®mb Č gu ukwarama, nawe m Čtaaririr…®!‚Äô 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄúN…®mbu na niimw…® m Čr…®, k Č k Čbha han Č Yoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi iizir…®, ataar…® ararya m…®kaat…® na kunywa idivaayi, na niimw…® m Čkabhuga ‚ÄėW Čn Č ana amasambwa!‚Äô  
\v 34 Umwana w Č …Ąm Č Čt Č akaaza, ararya ibhyakurya bhya amanar Č na kunywa idivaayi, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄėRora! N…®‚ÄĎm Čs Č Čh Č munywi, m Čsaani wa abharihya bha rig Č Čti, na bh Č  Čbh Čbh…®!‚Äô  
\v 35 Nawe n Č Čr Čbhu ubhw Čbh Č Čri bhwa Mungu bh Čhaamenyeekererya k Čbha n…®‚ÄĎmaheene k Čbhaat Č bhaaz…®.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su aramobheerera w Č  Čbh Čbh…® 
\p  
\v 36 Aar…® areho …Ąm Čfarisaayo w Čmw…® m Čr Čbh…®ri ororebhe. Rusik Č r Čmw…® akaraar…®ka Y…®…®su kurya …®waaz…®. Neho Y…®…®su akasik…®ra munyumba y Č …Ąm Čfarisaayo wuyo, akiikara kwigari.  
\v 37 Na m Čr Čbh…®ri ruyo, kwar…® n Č  Čm Čkari w Čmw…®, w Čn Č aam…®ny…®k…®…®n…® w Č  Čbh Čbh…®. Han Č  Čm Čkari wuyo, iigwir…® k Čbha Y…®…®su ararya w Č …Ąm Čfarisaayo, akasik…®ra muyo ani ichupa …®nz Čmu ya amaguta gan Č gakoreetya bhwaheene.  
\v 38 Akahigama haguh…® na amag Čr Č ga Y…®…®su, akatanga k Čr…®ra. Zingusuri zaaz…® z…®ragerera k Čmag Čr Č ga Y…®…®su, aar…® arazihuta na zinzw…®r…® zaaz…®, akahumbata amag Čr Č ga Y…®…®su, na k Čgahaka amaguta gayo. 
