\p Akam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúIriina ryan…®, n…®‚ÄĎBhasirikar…®.‚ÄĚ Akagambabhu, k Č k Čbha amasambwa maaru gaar…® gamusikiriir…®.  
\v 31 Amasambwa gayo, gakatanga kwisasaama Y…®…®su atagaswaja kuja mwir Č Čma rya nyaari.\f + \fr 8:31 \fk Nyaari\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* 
\p  
\v 32 Ahagero hayo kwar…® n…® …®k…®g Čr Č, na rusiz Č w…® …®k…®g Čr Č, ryareho rihiz Č ik Čr Č rya zingurubh…® r…®rariisha. Neho amasambwa gayo gakiisasaama Y…®…®su, agiisiririry…® gasik…®r…®r…® zingurubh…®. Y…®…®su akagiisiririrya.  
\v 33 Amasambwa gayo gakarw…®ku  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo, gakaja muzingurubh…®. Rihiz Č riyo r…®kahiringita mwega ikihiringint Č …®k…®haari z…®kagwa m Čmanzi z…®kakwa. 
