\v 34 Kwareho na abhariisha bha zingurubh…® ziyo. Abhariisha bhayo, bhaaza korora g Č Čsi gan Č gahurukir…®, bhakaryara, bhakaragan ľya amang ľana gayo m Čz…®mb…®ri.  
