\v 7 G Č Čsi gan Č Y…®…®su aar…® akokora,  Čm Čt…®mi Heroode Antipaasi aar…® ariigwa amang ľana gaaz…®, gakamoha ubhw Čbha. Ak Č Čbhaha k Č k Čbha abhaat Č abhand…® bhaar…® bharabhuga k Čbha, Y…®…®su newe Yoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi aryukir…® kurwa m Čbhaku.  
\v 8 Abhand…® bhaar…® bharabhuga k Čbha, newe  Čm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri ∆ó…®riya iizir…® naatu. Kwar…® na abhand…®, bhaar…® bharabhuga, w Čmw…® waho wa abhar Č Čt…®r…®ri bh…® …®kar…® newe aryukir…®. 
