\p  
\v 18 Rusik Č r Čmw…®, Y…®…®su aar…® arasabha Mungu haaw…®…®si na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhaar…® haguh…® nawe. Ak Čmara, akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúAbhaat Č bharabhuga iny…® n…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…®?‚ÄĚ 
