\v 19 Bhakam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúAbhand…® bharabhuga, aw…® ne‚ÄĎYoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi. Na abhand…® aw…®, n…®‚ÄĎ∆ó…®riya. N Č Čr Č abhand…® k Čbha aw…®, n…®‚ÄĎm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri w…® …®kar…® aryukir…®.‚ÄĚ 
