\p  
\v 1 Rusik Č r Čmw…®, Y…®…®su aar…® ahagero harebhe, arasabha Mungu. Han Č aamarir…®, w Čmw…® wa abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® akam Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č, utwij…® k Čsabha Mungu, ch…®mbu Yoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi abhiijiry…® abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®.‚ÄĚ 
