\v 28 Muyo n…®mbu, Mungu ahiibhohya bhwaheenebhu …®bh…®bhary Č bhya mwit…®r…®g Č bh…®n Č reero bhereho na tabh Č Čri bh…®rataashwa momorero. Nang Č, n…®‚ÄĎmaheene k…®mw…®k…®mw…® k Čbha arabhiibhohya imw…®, abhaat Č bhu ubhwisirirya ubhusuuhu! 
