\v 1 Ribhaga riyo, abhaat Č bhakabh Č Čr…®ra Y…®…®su, Piraato akiita Abhagariraaya abhand…®, ribhaga r…®n Č bhaar…® bhar…®…®tir…® imitug Č jabh Č g…®s…®nzw…®, gihurukibhw…® ikimweso kwa Mungu. 
