\p  
\v 1 Rusik Č r Čmw…®, abharihya bha rig Č Čti na bh Č  Čbh Čbh…®, bhaar…® bhariisuk…®ra Y…®…®su, bhamwitegeerere.  
\v 2 ∆ókagirya Abhafarisaayo na abhiija bhi imigir Č, bhakiibheerya bharabhuga, ‚Äú…Ąm Č Čt Č w Čn Č, ndora arabhaginihya bh Č  Čbh Čbh…®! Naatu ararya nabh Č!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 3 Neho Y…®…®su akabhaha ekerenjo, akabhuga,  
\v 4 ‚ÄúAw…®…®, w Čmw…® waanyu ana z…®ng ľ Čndu igana r…®mw…®. Araang ľur…® …®y…®mw…® yaho ibhurir…®, arakorabhw…®? Atakuzitiga merongo kenda na kenda mukiriish Č, na kuja komohya y…®n Č ibhurir…®, kuhika ayebhone?  
\v 5 Han Č araayebhone, arayegega k Čmabhega kwa bhozomerwa.  
\v 6 Han Č araahik…® y…®…®ka, arabhabh…®r…®k…®ra abhasaani bhaaz…® na bhanyar Čbh…®ri na k Čbhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄėTozomerwe hamw…®mw…®, k Č k Čbha …®ng ľ Čndu yaan…® y…®n Č yaabhurir…®, niyibhw…®n…®!‚Äô 
\p  
