\s1 Ekerenjo cha zimpirya z…®n Č zaabhurir…® 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúMwitegeerere ekerenjo …®k…®nd…®. …Ąm Čkari w Čmw…® ana amazenzere\f + \fr 15:8 \fk Amazenzere \ft kuKigiriki n…®‚ÄĎ\fqa darakima\ft . Darakima y…®mw…® yaar…® amarihi go omohocha kurusik Č r Čmw…®.\f* ikumi, na araabhury…® r…®mw…® arakorabhw…®? Atakugwatya …®k…®m Čr…®, na k Čtaricha inyumba y Č Čsi na komohya kwa managa kuhika ayebhone?  
\v 9 Han Č araayebhone, arabhabh…®r…®k…®ra abhasaani bhaaz…® na bhanyar Čbh…®ri, na k Čbhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄėTozomerwe hamw…®mw…®, k Č k Čbha impirya yaan…®, y…®n Č yaabhurir…®, niyibhw…®n…®!‚Äô 
