\v 46 Akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúYandikirw…® m ČMaand…®k Č Amar…®ndu, ‚ÄėInyumba yaan…®, …®rabha inyumba ya amasabhi.‚Äô\f + \fr 19:46a \xt Rora Isaaya 56:7.\f* Nawe imw…®, m Čy…®k Črir…® k Čbha ribhigi rya abhasaakuri.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 19:46b \xt Rora Y…®r…®miya 7:11.\f* 
