\v 9 Y…®…®su akang ľeha k Čbh Č Čr…®ra abhaat Č ekerenjo. Akabhuga, ‚ÄúKwar…® n Č  Čm Č Čt Č w Čmw…®, w Čn Č aahambir…® …®m…®zabhiibhu m Čm Čg Čnd Č gwaz…®, akak Č Čdishirya abharimi. Ewe akaja ichar Č …®k…®nd…®, akamara iyo sik Č nzaru.  
\v 10 Na han Č zisik Č zo okogesa zaahikir…®, akat Čma mb Č Čsa waaz…® k Čbharimi bhayo, korereke bhamohe ribhaara ryaz…® ryi ibhyakurya, agar Čk…® nary Č k Čm Čk Čr Č waaz…®. Nawe, han Č mb Č Čsa aahikir…®, abharimi bhayo bhakamotema na bhakamoheebha mabhoko bh Č Čha. 
