\v 17 Y…®…®su akabhakandikija am…®…®s Č, akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúNang Č! Amaand…®k Č gan Č gana nzobhoorok…®? 
\q1 ‚ÄėRiibhw…® r…®n Č abh Č Čmbaki bhaangir…®, 
\q1 neryo r…®bh…®…®r…® riibhw…® rik Čr Č rya rusiz Č.‚Äô\f + \fr 20:17 \fk Riibhw…® rik Čr Č rya rusiz Č \ft ryar…® rereenderwa kury Čmbaka rya Abhayaahudi. R…®kagwatan ľya nyiki ibh…®r…® na kugwat…®r…®ra inyumba ngima. \xt Rora Zabhuri 118:22.\f* 
\m  
\v 18 …Ąm Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č ak Čbha agwiriir…® riibhw…® riyo, arabhun…®kabhun…®ka. Na w Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č riibhw…® riyo r…®raamugw…®r…®, r…®ramusha bhoseeseka.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 19 Abhiija bhi imigir Č bhayo na abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani, bhakamenya k Čbha, ekerenjo kiyo nebho k…®k Čgamb…®ra. Bhakeenda kumugwata hayohayo, nawe bhak Č Čbhaha riribhita rya abhaat Č. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhuuribhwa ig Čr Č w Č  Čk Čr…®ha rig Č Čti 
