\p  
\v 1 Han Č Y…®…®su aar…® mwihekaaru, akabharora abhaniibhi bharat Č Čra ikimweso chabh Č mokegero chu ukuhurukirya ikimweso.  
\v 2 Naatu akarora umukwirwa w Čmw…®  Čm Čhabh…®, arat Č Čra amazenzere abh…®r…®. 
\p  
\v 3 Y…®…®su akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®rabhabh Č Čr…®ra n…®‚ÄĎmaheene, umukwirwa  Čm Čhabh…® w Čn Č, newe ahurukiry…® zimpirya nzaru k Čk…®ra bh Č Čsi bhan Č bhahurukiry…®.  
\v 4 N…®rabhugabhu, k Č k Čbha bhan Č bh Č Čsi bhahurukiry…®, ikimweso k…®n Č bhahurukiry…®, n…®‚ÄĎhagero hasuuhu he ebhegero bhyabh Č ibhyaru. Nawe umukwirwa w Čn Č  Čm Čhabh…®, ahurukiry…® bhy Čsi bh…®n Č aar…® anabhy Č mubhwikari bhwaz…®!‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su aragamb…®ra  Čk Čsaribhwa kwa rihekaaru 
\r (Mataayo 24:1‚ÄĎ2; Maaroko 13:1‚ÄĎ2) 
