\p  
\v 36 Y…®…®su akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúNawe nang Č, w…® …®k…®g Čzi cha zimpirya agege, na w…® …®sakwa, agege, na w Čn Č ataana risabha, agury…® …®kabhuuti yaaz…®, korereke ag Čr…® risabha.  
\v 37 Mokorebhu k Č k Čbha ribhaga r…®raariir…®, amang ľana gan Č gaandikirw…® m ČMaand…®k Č Amar…®ndu gakorwe, k Čbha ‚ÄėAkabharwa hamw…®mw…® na abhak Čri bha amabh…®.‚Äô Amaheene amang ľana gan Č gaandikirw…® ig Čr Č waan…® gareenderwa gakorwe.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 38 Bhakam Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č! Rora! Han Č gareho amasabha abh…®r…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p Akabhuga, ‚ÄúYiisir…®.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su arasabha Mungu k Čk…®g Čr Č ch…® ∆óm…®z…®yituuni 
\r (Mataayo 26:36‚ÄĎ46; Maaroko 14:32‚ÄĎ42) 
\p  
\v 39 Ribhaga riyo Y…®…®su akarwa hayo, akaja k Čk…®g Čr Č ch…® ∆óm…®z…®yituuni ch…®mbu amanar Č gaaz…®, na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhakamutuna.  
\v 40 Akahika k Čk…®g Čr Č kiyo akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúM Čsabh…® Mungu m Čtaaza kusik…®ra mubhitiimotiimo.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 41 Akabhatiga hayo, akiisuka embere hasuuhu, ch…®mbu obhokore bhw Č  Čk Čtaasha riibhw…®, akahigama akasabha Mungu,  
\v 42 ‚ÄúBhaabha! Ar…®…®bh…®  Čs…®…®gir…®, n…®rak Čsabha unduushiry…® ekekombe ch…® …®nyaak Č k…®n Č. ∆ótar…® ch…®mbu iny…® nikwenda, nawe gakorwe ch…®mbu aw…® ukwenda.‚ÄĚ [ 
\v 43 Hayo, maraika kurwa mwisaar Č akah Čr Čk…®ra Y…®…®su, akamoha zinguru.  
\v 44 Y…®…®su akabha n Č  Čbh Čs Čng Č bh Čhaari bh Čk Čng ľu, akang ľeha k Čsabha Mungu. ∆ók…®t Čg Čta chaz…®, k…®katoonya haas…® kituubh…®…®n…® na amasaah…®.] 
\p  
\v 45 Han Č aamarir…® k Čsabha, akiim…®…®r…®ra, akagar Čk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, akabhona bhahindiir…® k Č k Čbha bhaar…® bharumikir…®.  
\v 46 Akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúHeene! Kwak…® muhindiir…®? M Čbh Č Čk…® m Čsabh…®, m Čtaaza kusik…®ra mubhitiimotiimo.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su aragwatwa 
