\v 54 Neho abhaat Č bhayo bhakagwata Y…®…®su, bhakaja nawe kuhika munyumba ya kuhaani  Čm Čk Čr Č.\f + \fr 22:54 \fk Kuhaani  Čm Čk Čr Č\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora ring ľana \ft \+it abhakuhaani\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* Peetero aar…® aratuna Y…®…®su kwa kore.  
\v 55 Han Č bhaahikir…® k Čr Čbh Č Čga rwi inyumba omorero g Čkaakibhwa, bhakiikara. Peetero w Č Čsi, akaaza kwikara rusiz Č waabh Č.  
\v 56 Omohocha w Čmw…® w…® …®k…®kari akamomogorera, akabhuga, ‚Äú…Ąm Č Čt Č w Čn Č, aar…® hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su.‚ÄĚ 
