\v 67 ‚ÄúAr…®…®bh…® aw…® naaw…® Kiriisit Č, t Čbh Č Čr…®r…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p Akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúN Č Čr Č n…®raabhabh Č Čr…®r…®, m Čtakwisirirya,  
\v 68 na n…®rabhabhuury…®, m Čtak Čngarukirya.  
\v 69 Nawe kw…®ma nang Č, Umwana w Č …Ąm Č Čt Č arabha ik…®…®r…®  Čr Čbhaara rwu ubhury Č rwa Mungu wa zinguru.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 22:69 \xt Rora Zabhuri 110:1.\f* 
\p  
\v 70 Bh Č Čsi bhakamubhuurya, ‚ÄúHeene aw…® ni‚ÄĎMwana wa Mungu?‚ÄĚ 
\p Y…®…®su akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúNdora imubheene m Čmarir…® k Čgamba k Čbha iny…® newe!‚ÄĚ 
