\v 45 k Č k Čbha iry Čbha r…®karima. Na ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru,\f + \fr 23:45 \fk Ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru \ft riyo ryar…® mwihekaaru, r…®rak…®nga abhaat Č bhatasik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu, han Č ubhw…®r Č bhwa Mungu bhwik…®…®r…®. \xt Rora Abh…®…®bhuraaniya 6:19, 10:19‚ÄĎ22. \ft K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora ring ľana \ft \+it rihekaaru\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* rogendo r Čmw…® r…®kabhaar Čka mbaara ibh…®r…®! 
